{"tid":804702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵放寛南韓鋼鐵關稅後 浦項鋼鐵擴大投資404億美元","createTime":"2018-09-03T08:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T08:33:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7ef56de8f622d936eecab19d4614af63d98019","tid":804702,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"川普上週三簽署一份「限定配額」豁免部分國家鋼鐵鋁的公文過後，受惠其中南韓鋼鐵頓時壓力驟減。<br />\n<br />\n在川普放寬鋼鐵鋁關稅政策後，為了提高鋼鐵業的競爭力，韓國鋼鐵製造商浦項鋼鐵 (POSCO) 今 (3 日) 日表示，將在未來五年內投資 45 兆韓元 (404 億美元)，用於更新和增加鋼鐵設備，以及鋰電池在內的新業務部門。<br />\n<br />\n浦項鋼鐵在聲明中表示，POSCO 將在 2023 年內投資 26 兆韓元用於升級和增加鋼鐵設施、10 兆韓元用於包括鋰電池在內的新業務部門、其餘資金用於能源業務。<br />\n<br />\n根據該公司的數據，計劃在未來五年內將總支出提高 27 兆韓元至 45 兆韓元，相當於過去五年支出 18 兆韓元的兩倍半。<br />\n<br />\n近來浦項鋼鐵積極布局全球產業鏈，著眼於新興國家的鋼鐵產業需求，好比汽車、能源、家電等，進行針對性的海外投資。<br />\n<br />\n8 月下旬，浦項鋼鐵與澳洲銀河資源 (Galaxy Resources) 簽訂不具約束力的協議，以 2.8 億美元的價格購買其在阿根廷北部的鋰礦項目。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國商務部上週三 (8 月 29 日) 表示，美國總統川普已批准一份針對性豁免部分國家鋼鐵和鋁配額的公文，允許韓國、巴西和阿根廷鋼鐵鋁產品，在限定關稅配額內可豁免關稅。目前韓國鋼鐵每年最多出口約 270 萬噸。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n豁免鋼鐵消息公布後，全球第四大鋼鐵製造商浦項鋼鐵 (005490-KW)8 月 30 日一度大漲至每股 341000 韓元，然而，今大舉投資消息傳出，市場卻反應冷淡，下跌 2.14%，暫報每股 319500 韓元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4194926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4194926&d=RFr6eMAmjhJIS1gb9w5pjUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e4cb404b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4194926</a>"},{"pid":"a974380e8bf441dc267c616b0fe4d64c8aa0810f","tid":804702,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"支那冇份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107bb71cf7139528552d9b778e5f55b715b45fa3","tid":804702,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"日本呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcbf86f4e9d233b491ba1517a4144975e5113cf","tid":804702,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"107bb71cf7139528552d9b778e5f55b715b45fa3","tid":804702,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"日本呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"贏国而家成日吹奏中日友好<br />\n日本小心唔好中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09872958bfb30faf634d24e62b980ef2224d1cb","tid":804702,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fcbf86f4e9d233b491ba1517a4144975e5113cf","tid":804702,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"107bb71cf7139528552d9b778e5f55b715b45fa3","tid":804702,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"日本呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"贏国而家成日吹奏中日友好<br />\n日本小心唔好中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本首相說中日關係完全回歸正軌，副首相：並不是聯中抗美<br />\n<br />\n【文/觀察者網 徐乾昂】「中日關係已經完全回到正軌。」<br />\n<br />\n今年是《中日和平友好條約》締結40周年，兩國高層近期頻繁互訪。中日財長第七次對話剛剛結束，日本首相安倍晉三就在《產經新聞》2日的專訪中做出上述表態。<br />\n<br />\n也有媒體認為，中日關係升溫的背後少不了美國的「神助攻」。但《產經新聞》3日「搬出」日本副首相麻生太郎在8月31日說法進行「平衡」，麻生當時否認「日本聯中抗美」一說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xuehua.us/2018/09/03/%E4%BB%96%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%A5%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%9E%E5%BD%92%E6%AD%A3%E8%BD%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%89%AF%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%EF%BC%9A%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%81%94%E4%B8%AD/zh-tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xuehua.us%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F%25E4%25BB%2596%25E8%25AF%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25B3%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25BD%2592%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25BD%25A8%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%2589%25AF%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B9%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%2581%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%2Fzh-tw%2F&d=RFr6eMAmjhJIS1gb9w5pjUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e2ad5f93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xuehua.us/2018/09/03/%E4%BB%96%E8%AF%B4%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%A5%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%9E%E5%BD%92%E6%AD%A3%E8%BD%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%89%AF%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%EF%BC%9A%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%81%94%E4%B8%AD/zh-tw/</a>"}]}